{"id":3059,"date":"2021-08-27T14:25:25","date_gmt":"2021-08-27T14:25:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/dienlanhvineco.com\/?p=3059"},"modified":"2021-08-31T07:47:04","modified_gmt":"2021-08-31T07:47:04","slug":"sua-bep-tu-chefs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/dienlanhvineco.com\/sua-bep-tu-chefs\/","title":{"rendered":"S\u1eecA B\u1ebeP T\u1eea CHEFS"},"content":{"rendered":"<blockquote><p><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 110%;\"><strong>S\u1eecA B\u1ebeP T\u1eea CHEFS<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 110%;\"><em><strong>Trung t\u00e2m b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh s\u1eeda b\u1ebfp t\u1eeb Chefs t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 110%;\">Trung t\u00e2m b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh <a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/dienlanhvineco.com\/sua-bep-tu-chefs\/\">s\u1eeda b\u1ebfp t\u1eeb Chefs ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/a>. V\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n mang \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh b\u1ebfp t\u1eeb Chefs t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, linh ki\u1ec7n ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng, ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh sau s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n nh\u1ea5t. Trung t\u00e2m b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i b\u1ebfp t\u1eeb Chefs ph\u00e1t sinh khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3060 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/dienlanhvineco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/bep-dien-tu-Chefs-3vung-nau-600x600-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dienlanhvineco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/bep-dien-tu-Chefs-3vung-nau-600x600-1.jpg 600w, https:\/\/dienlanhvineco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/bep-dien-tu-Chefs-3vung-nau-600x600-1-45x45.jpg 45w, https:\/\/dienlanhvineco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/bep-dien-tu-Chefs-3vung-nau-600x600-1-510x